    "body": "## Purpose\n\n  Add benchmark to measure VLLM_BATCH_INVARIANT mode performance overhead.\n\n<details>\n      <summary> Qwen/Qwen3-1.7B is comparable</summary>\n\n```\n================================================================================\nVLLM BATCH INVARIANCE BENCHMARK\n================================================================================\nConfiguration:\n  Model: Qwen/Qwen3-1.7B\n  Tensor Parallel Size: 1\n  Attention Backend: FLASHINFER\n  Max Batch Size: 128\n  Number of Trials: 5\n  Prompt Length Range: 1024-2048 words\n  Max Tokens to Generate: 128\n  Temperature: 0.0\n  GPU Memory Utilization: 0.4\n  Max Model Length: 5120\n================================================================================\n================================================================================\nCOMPARISON: Batch Invariance vs Baseline\n================================================================================\nInitialization Time:\n  Baseline:         98.85s\n  Batch Invariant:  18.67s\n  Overhead:         -81.12%\nAverage Trial Time:\n  Baseline:         0.77s\n  Batch Invariant:  0.77s\n  Overhead:         +0.85%\nThroughput (tokens/s):\n  Baseline:         15713.46\n  Batch Invariant:  15617.86\n  Change:           -0.61%\nPrompts/s:\n  Baseline:         123.05\n  Batch Invariant:  122.01\n================================================================================\n```\n\n</details>\n<details>\n      <summary> deepseek-ai/DeepSeek-V3 is much slower (3x) currently </summary>\n\n```\n================================================================================\nVLLM BATCH INVARIANCE BENCHMARK\n================================================================================\nConfiguration:\n  Model: deepseek-ai/DeepSeek-V3\n  Tensor Parallel Size: 8\n  Attention Backend: FLASH_ATTN_MLA\n  Max Batch Size: 128\n  Number of Trials: 5\n  Prompt Length Range: 1024-2048 words\n  Max Tokens to Generate: 128\n  Temperature: 0.0\n  GPU Memory Utilization: 0.9\n  Max Model Length: 5120\n================================================================================\n================================================================================\nCOMPARISON: Batch Invariance vs Baseline\n================================================================================\nInitialization Time:\n  Baseline:         112.36s\n  Batch Invariant:  200.15s\n  Overhead:         +78.13%\nAverage Trial Time:\n  Baseline:         4.49s\n  Batch Invariant:  13.37s\n  Overhead:         +197.70%\nThroughput (tokens/s):\n  Baseline:         552.90\n  Batch Invariant:  185.73\n  Change:           -66.41%\nPrompts/s:\n  Baseline:         4.32\n  Batch Invariant:  1.45\n================================================================================\n```\n\n</details>\n<details>\n      <summary> deepseek-ai/DeepSeek-V3 improves when removing the legacy override (using torch.compile) </summary>\n\n```\n================================================================================\nVLLM BATCH INVARIANCE BENCHMARK\n================================================================================\nConfiguration:\n  Model: deepseek-ai/DeepSeek-V3\n  Tensor Parallel Size: 8\n  Attention Backend: FLASH_ATTN_MLA\n  Max Batch Size: 32\n  Number of Trials: 5\n  Prompt Length Range: 1024-2048 words\n  Max Tokens to Generate: 128\n  Temperature: 0.0\n  GPU Memory Utilization: 0.9\n  Max Model Length: 5120\n================================================================================\n================================================================================\nCOMPARISON: Batch Invariance vs Baseline\n================================================================================\nInitialization Time:\n  Baseline:         116.74s\n  Batch Invariant:  108.36s\n  Overhead:         -7.18%\nAverage Trial Time:\n  Baseline:         4.69s\n  Batch Invariant:  10.91s\n  Overhead:         +132.49%\nThroughput (tokens/s):\n  Baseline:         529.16\n  Batch Invariant:  227.60\n  Change:           -56.99%\nPrompts/s:\n  Baseline:         4.13\n  Batch Invariant:  1.78\n================================================================================\n```\n\n</details>\n\n  ## Test Plan\n\n  ```bash\n  # Default (Qwen3-1.7B)\n  python benchmarks/benchmark_batch_invariance.py\n\n  # DeepSeek-V3 with TP=8\n  VLLM_BENCH_MODEL=\"deepseek-ai/DeepSeek-V3\" VLLM_BENCH_TP_SIZE=8 VLLM_BENCH_GPU_MEMORY_UTILIZATION=0.9 python benchmarks/benchmark_batch_invariance.py\n\n  Test Result\n\n  Benchmark runs and reports throughput comparison between batch invariant mode vs baseline.\n",
